# Excludes heavy/unnecessary paths from the Docker build context.
# This speeds up builds and prevents the host's node_modules from
# being copied into the image (which would conflict with the container's
# own pnpm install). Note: this does NOT affect runtime volume mounts.

node_modules
.next
out
.git
.gitignore
*.md
.env*
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
